[17.7, "o", "\u001b[1mWhy PostgreSQL instead of MongoDB?\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[17.8, "o", "\u001b[2m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[17.9, "o", "\r\n"]
[18.0, "o", "The switch to PostgreSQL (PR #234, March 2022) was driven by the need for ACID\r\n"]
[18.3, "o", "transactions in financial record processing. The team evaluated two alternatives:\r\n"]
[18.6, "o", "\r\n"]
[18.7, "o", "  \u001b[31m✗\u001b[0m \u001b[1mMongoDB\u001b[0m — rejected: lack of multi-document transactions caused data integrity\r\n"]
[18.9, "o", "    failures in the order pipeline (Issue #189)\r\n"]
[19.1, "o", "  \u001b[31m✗\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCockroachDB\u001b[0m — rejected: operational overhead too high at team's scale\r\n"]
[19.3, "o", "\r\n"]
[19.4, "o", "  Trade-offs accepted: ~2 weeks migration effort, higher baseline memory usage.\r\n"]
[19.6, "o", "\r\n"]
[19.7, "o", "  \u001b[2mSources: PR #234, Issue #189, commit a3f9c12\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[19.8, "o", "\r\n"]
