[29.7, "o", "\u001b[1;33m⚠  CONFLICT DETECTED\u001b[0m  \u001b[41;37m HIGH \u001b[0m\r\n"]
[29.8, "o", "\u001b[2m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[29.9, "o", "\r\n"]
[30.0, "o", "In PR #234 (2022-03-15), the team explicitly rejected MongoDB for session storage\r\n"]
[30.3, "o", "due to lack of ACID transactions. This proposal directly contradicts that decision.\r\n"]
[30.6, "o", "\r\n"]
[30.7, "o", "  \u001b[1mConflicting decision:\u001b[0m PostgreSQL Migration (PR #234) · confidence 0.94\r\n"]
[30.9, "o", "  \u001b[1mSuggested action:\u001b[0m   Review the migration decision and update it if the context\r\n"]
[31.1, "o", "                    has changed before proceeding.\r\n"]
